{
  "title": "Progression to third birth in Morocco in the context of fertility transition",
  "abstract": "Progression from second to third birth is a critical reproductive decision in contemporary Morocco. The study thus aims at analyzing the main determinants of third-birth intensities, applying an event-history analysis to the most recent Moroccan survey",
